      "role": "user",
      "content": "sometimes i sit here in my apartment and it feels like i dont even exist. like i'm just a ghost. i work, i eat, i sleep, but if i just... stopped? if i just drifted away and stopped showing up online or responding to anything? i don't think anyone would even realize i was gone for weeks.",
